{"tid":1002830,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"德國教師指責中國：中國的教育本身就是犯罪","createTime":"2019-01-31T08:21:02.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-31T12:50:22.000Z","uid":22675,"like":102,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"1876ff5d01d94c84e9d222529f563ae6b1238749","tid":1002830,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-31T08:21:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i2.wp.com/hkjam.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/sketch-1548066475810.png?resize=1024%2C576\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi2.wp.com%2Fhkjam.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F01%2Fsketch-1548066475810.png%3Fresize%3D1024%252C576&h=f27028b7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n一名叫西洛特的德國教師到中國進行教育工作一段短暫的時間之後，決定辭職回國。在仔他眼中，中國的教育等同犯罪，他表明不希望參與，更接受傳媒訪問，力數中國教育的邪惡之處。<br />\n<br />\n他表示，中國的學校經常向學生灌輸愛國主義口號，但卻沒有鼓勵學生關懷社會，培養人文精神，他質疑這只是洗腦，不會令人真心愛國。最可怕的是這些教條式的愛國口號，正正是試卷上的標準答案，不容學生否定或質疑。<br />\n<br />\n西洛特又指責中國的扭曲教育觀念令學生變得短視和急功近利。人性、道德和邏輯卻成為了空白，沒有形成健全人格，導致各種社會問題叢生。<br />\n<br />\n他認為中國的主流教育正在摧毀學生，也在摧毀一個社會，教育本身就是罪惡，是對人類天性的殘害。"},{"pid":"ff0330460e5b04456b4e09a448d18093df584ec5","tid":1002830,"uid":61280,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-31T08:21:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fbb396f7d0820b3a906326346598bf1966e4d2cd","tid":1002830,"uid":56015,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-31T08:22:44.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hkjam.com/?p=12662#\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkjam.com%2F%3Fp%3D12662%23&d=h41GIreLF%2BIJLuW8J2uc6uBrFmK%2FfjgW9YhWFGnkYF4%3D&h=777efa7f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hkjam.com/?p=12662#</a>"},{"pid":"b317b3f0a3aee72eb13438654469fbf1e5b832ed","tid":1002830,"uid":5162