0Z","msg":"講得好中"},{"pid":"e571e949fbb6cdbf1c28b4e2b2797af0f3250e4b","tid":1002830,"uid":36494,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0173937ba271492168502b3761cea766ea3ef078","tid":1002830,"uid":74778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-31T08:31:53.000Z","msg":"農民定出黎制度<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-31T08:42:48.000Z","msg":"唔關係咪農民事<br />\n<br />\n而係中共任何政策，最終目的都係為咗維護佢個政權不被挑戰，所以教育一定係洗腦式以擁護共産黨為先"},{"pid":"7badc6799aaf8826c5c1bdf05d972fe1d9ebb362","tid":1002830,"uid":179908,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-31T08:44:29.000Z","msg":"當年諗一國兩制<br />\n唔諗呢啲港中差異既人真係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n中國人好多問題係教育問題造成"},{"pid":"c6589d7cf99d5e7be128805a5225327f4b9ecf33","tid":1002830,"uid":63909,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-31T08:47:49.000Z","msg":"德國教師果然正氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"345e70c7b7cb21f90f670f5ac8658c7c2ead40f5","tid":1002830,"uid":41477,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-31T08:52:36.000Z","msg":"其實一樣,當你教育已經爛到咁時,再做任何公益關懷宣傳,大家都會當你係虛偽"},{"pid":"38b5b434d3bcc09391fd08468b80acfd8ebe0b71","tid":1002830,"uid":6222,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-31T09:04:24.000Z","msg":"他表示，中國的學校經常向學生灌輸愛國主義口號，但卻沒有鼓勵學生關懷社會，培養人文精神，他質疑這只是洗腦，不會令人真心愛國。<br />\n<br />\n請得好<br />\n<br />\n班支那人只係口講愛國<br />\n<br />\n係自己地方都照隨地吐痰 亂拋垃圾 周街痾屎痾尿<br />\n<br />\n乜依D行為係愛國咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"53b324e8ebe6522934b8745b4b79cc44fc53e822","tid":1002830,"uid":60635,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"b317b3f0a3aee72eb13438654469fbf1e5b832ed","tid":1002830,"uid":51625,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-31T08:23:38.000Z","msg":"香港都係一樣"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-31T09:55:41.000Z","msg":"睇下班廢老廢中受完香港教育瘋狂殘害社會<img s